 Conclusion

The nutrition dataset was successfully loaded, inspected, cleaned, and analyzed using Pandas. Missing values were identified and removed to improve data quality. Basic statistical analysis was performed to calculate the average and maximum values and identify the location with the highest average Data_Value. These results provide useful insights into the nutritional measurements recorded in the dataset.
